title: #167: The Tin Foil Ripple Farm Report Swapcast Chapter 2
description: Thank you for tuning in for another episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli.  This week I did another installment of the Tin Foil Ripple Farm Report swap cast with James Corbett,  Ricky Varandas  and eventually Pat Miletech.  It's always a pleasure to talk to these guys about what is really going on in the world. Thank you for your support.
